OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771916638
OL,3,CPhoto of Andrew after his arrest
OL,4,Cmounted on a wall in the Louvre
OL,6,FAn iconic image of Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,7,FWindsor after his arrest has been
OL,8,F"hung" in the Louvre by activists.
OL,10,FAnti-billionaire group Everyone Hates
OL,11,FElon mounted the photo on a wall
OL,12,Finside the Paris art museum on Sunday.
OL,14,FIn a message to ITV News, the group
OL,15,Fwrote: "They say: 'Hang it in the
OL,16,FLouvre'. So we did.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
