PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771916638
OL,3,CPhoto of Andrew after his arrest
OL,4,Cmounted on a wall in the Louvre
OL,6,F"We wanted to show the former Prince
OL,7,FAndrew how the world will remember him
OL,8,F- by hanging this iconic arrest photo
OL,9,Fin one of the world's most famous
OL,10,Fmuseums.
OL,12,F"Let's hope this is just the
OL,13,Fbeginning."
OL,15,FEveryone Hates Elon uploaded a video
OL,16,Fto social media, showing the
OL,17,Fphotograph mounted on a wall in the
OL,18,FLouvre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
