PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771916638
OL,3,CPhoto of Andrew after his arrest
OL,4,Cmounted on a wall in the Louvre
OL,6,FIt was on display for around an hour
OL,7,Fbefore being taken down, according to
OL,8,Fthe group.
OL,10,FThe Louvre museum has said it will not
OL,11,Fcomment on the incident.
OL,13,FAccompanying the photo was a caption
OL,14,Freading "He's Sweating Now",
OL,15,Freferencing a BBC interview in 2019
OL,16,Fwhere the former prince attempted to
OL,17,Fdefend himself against allegations of
OL,18,Fsexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
