PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771916638
OL,3,CPhoto of Andrew after his arrest
OL,4,Cmounted on a wall in the Louvre
OL,6,FResponding to an accuser saying he had
OL,7,Fbeen "profusely sweating" on the night
OL,8,Fof his alleged crime, Mountbatten-
OL,9,FWindsor said he has a "peculiar
OL,10,Fmedical condition" which makes him
OL,11,Funable to sweat.
OL,13,FAndrew has consistently denied any
OL,14,Fwrongdoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
